<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Merci - Dossier Enregistré</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 128 128%22><text y=%221.2em%22 font-size=%2296%22>✅</text></svg>">
    {% block stylesheets %}
        {{ importmap('app') }}
    {% endblock %}
    <style>
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f4ff 0%, #e8f0fe 100%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }

        .success-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 48px rgba(13,110,253,0.12);
            padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
            max-width: 560px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .icon-wrapper {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d6efd, #6ea8fe);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 1.75rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(13,110,253,0.35);
        }

        .success-card h1 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .success-card .subtitle {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #6c757d;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .steps-box {
            background: #f8faff;
            border: 1.5px solid #dce8ff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .steps-box .steps-title {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            color: #0d6efd;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .step-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 0.85rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
        }
        .step-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

        .step-num {
            width: 26px;
            height: 26px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d6efd, #6ea8fe);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #fff;
            margin-top: 1px;
        }

        .step-text {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #495057;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .step-text strong { color: #1a1a2e; }

        .close-hint {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #adb5bd;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="success-card">

    <div class="icon-wrapper">
        <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
        </svg>
    </div>

    <h1>Dossier enregistré !</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
        Merci d'avoir complété les informations.<br>
        Elles ont bien été transmises au lycée Gabriel Fauré.
    </p>

    <div class="steps-box">
        <div class="steps-title">Suite du processus</div>

        <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-num">1</div>
            <div class="step-text"><strong>Validation pédagogique</strong> — Le professeur référent de l'étudiant examine la collecte.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-num">2</div>
            <div class="step-text"><strong>Validation administrative</strong> — La DDF vérifie et valide les informations.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-num">3</div>
            <div class="step-text"><strong>Signature électronique</strong> — Vous recevrez la convention finale par email pour la signer.</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p class="close-hint">Vous pouvez fermer cette fenêtre en toute sécurité.</p>

</div>

</body>
</html>
